Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天的风真舒适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被蚊子咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真漫长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是止痒药喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最近看你总是很痒的样子 就带过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:01:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢… 谢谢
