Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是这么一回事 你也会来海边对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好热 好麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别这么说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学很期待呢 所以拜托啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一会要让你们独处 一会又要陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也替每次都被随意使唤的我想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过 你嘴上这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实是很喜欢照顾别人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你再得意忘形我就真的不管了你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对… 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 还有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你知道山岸同学的联络方式吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊？ 为什么我会知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也想邀请山岸同学 可是没有联络方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将吾小学跟她同班
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我想你应该知道她的联系方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小学时留的联系方式好像还在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不愧是将吾 真可靠 那就拜托…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和香织她们去海边？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 我去我去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就这样 明天拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 我有一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是忘了就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}希望你明天早上再联络我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拜托你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还真是被随意使唤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说回来 为什么他会知道我家的电话号码呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兴奋过头了 昨晚都没怎么睡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是远足前的小屁孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早上好 长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨天太兴奋了 没睡好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}同一类人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}桐生同学 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你们两位今天过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们才应该道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢你邀请我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}接下来就剩山岸同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}该不会忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这不可能 刚才出门的时候联络过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 香织
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好想你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沙希
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}发现放了暑假就暂时见不到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我好寂寞喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天让我好好撒娇喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个… 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从来都在的两位男生也好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}难道现在还没记住名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}根本就不打算记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么出发～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等一下 你把行李忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们俩 来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}差点坐上反方向的电车了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么只是坐个电车就这么累人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快来快来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天出来得早 我想着大家是不是没吃早饭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不介意的话请用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了 其实我很饿的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织真的很擅长料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学吃章鱼香肠是从腿开始吃的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的 把脸的部分留下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然日记里有写
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的是会先把腿吃完的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这… 这种事日记里都有写啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是为什么从腿开始吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从脸的部分开始吃感觉不怎么好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学好不容易做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感觉很可惜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能听你这么说我很高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一到海边就下雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没办法 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 为什么这么倒霉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.93,0:08:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还以为能在海里游泳的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雨这么大没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 下海太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 要被吹走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特别是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的很危险的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那在沙滩上玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走吧 香织
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来堆个沙雕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}水份太多有点难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她们两个像小孩子一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但只要藤宫同学乐在其中的话就再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说我们两个完全成监护人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好厉害啊 沙希
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}接下来玩球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学我上了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等 风太大…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要被冲走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我才说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给你 球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学湿透了呢 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算了 无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}反正是夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给 毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不快点擦干的话会感冒的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}毛巾的正确递法是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我给你紧紧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.96,0:10:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暂时在这里避雨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我第一次来游戏中心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.49,0:10:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有什么想玩的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我教你怎么玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然我不擅长抓娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在必须展示一下我帅气的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这次一定成功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就差一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.93,0:11:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抓娃娃好难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好厉害啊 桐生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是碰巧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你这家伙真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}接下来玩什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想玩射击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}射击… 将吾射击玩得很好来着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织 想拍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 有点憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那四个人一起拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吧 将吾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 我还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将吾说他也想拍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\blur0\bord0\pos(632,466)\fn经典中圆简\c&H000000&}请放入硬币
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要拍了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}开始了喔 3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}过来过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 感觉拍得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将吾果然不会笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\3c&H6BBCE7&\an8}大家都是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了 藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有长谷同学在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有沙希在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有桐生同学也在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}像这样和大家一起过暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}觉得自己真幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我很喜欢这张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}会把它当作宝贝的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雨 好像停了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好漂亮啊 大海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}风平浪静的 感觉真好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 对不起 肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}坐这吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}便当当早饭吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去买来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那来决定谁去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 来猜拳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:13:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为啥！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁让你想出用猜拳决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我们去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呐呐 喜欢香织哪里啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你突然说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长相？性格？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才没用那种奇怪的眼光去看待藤宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是单纯作为朋友在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我经常抱着她所以知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胸部很大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能下海 太遗憾啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说山岸同学 不要玩弄别人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}买哪个好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}随便买点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}变得不那么战战兢兢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:14:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说啊 藤宫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是怎么看待那家伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那家伙是指长谷同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么看待… 他是很重要的朋友喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 虽然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}前阵子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看着长谷和别人聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胸口稍微有点焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别人是指女生？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 为什么你会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还为什么… 那当然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}买这些就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听我说啊 我买了好东西喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看 等天再黑一点 我们来放烟花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个贝壳很漂亮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 这里有个更大的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一开始还真是有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是藤宫同学似乎很开心真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说你 就这样下去真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？ 你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再进一步不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学 玩得开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊… 嗯 很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呐呐 有寄居蟹喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么大的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.35,0:16:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可不信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的啊 在这里喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.03,0:17:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呐 去散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天真是充满了笑声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早知如此 就应该早点邀请你们来海边的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么一直开不了口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微下海看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学也过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大海真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果不下雨就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也很喜欢雨喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大海和夕阳 都非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是不会忘记今天的事情就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}炎热的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}炎热的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}烟花耀眼地燃烧着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这份炎热依旧没有褪去的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}借我点个火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大海也看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也在沙滩上玩过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:20:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还第一次去了游戏厅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还放了烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一次度过一个这么充实的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽说是充实的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过也只是在一天里发生的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非常喜欢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}烟花真不错啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最近常常会想用「喜欢」这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是一个什么现象呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好热
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还打算在北海道待到天气转凉再回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天要把行李都卸下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了 快点进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.34,0:21:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又回来了啊 东京
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.69,0:23:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和朋友一起度过的最后一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.47,0:23:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
